.Sh EXAMPLES
To build the native targets for a bundle with no additional arguments:
.Bd -literal -offset indent
$ jeep build
.Ed
.Pp
To build the native targets for a bundle with additional arguments:
.Bd -literal -offset indent
$ jeep build -Dfoo -Dbar
.Ed
.Pp
Note that your build function will need to parse the arguments
passed to it.
